author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-1347 Property Insurance Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.23
text:
March 26 (Reuters) - 1347 Property Insurance Holdings Inc :
* 1347 PROPERTY INSURANCE HOLDINGS, INC. ANNOUNCES 2017 FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR FINANCIAL RESULTS
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.23 * BOOK VALUE PER SHARE OF $7.82 AT DECEMBER 31, 2017 VERSUS $7.62 AT SEPTEMBER 30, 2017
* QTRLY NET PREMIUMS EARNED INCREASED 34.2% TO $10.2 MILLION FROM $7.6 MILLION
* Q4 ‍ GROSS PREMIUMS WRITTEN OF $23.9 MILLION, UP 101.5% FROM $11.8 MILLION IN PRIOR-YEAR QUARTER​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
